<!-- ============================================================ -->
<!-- 1. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY -->
<!-- ============================================================ -->

<h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>

<p>The <b>Advisory AI Ideas</b> application is a Microsoft Power Apps Canvas App that provides KPMG Advisory with a centralised platform for managing AI use-case ideas and a curated AI prompt library. The app is backed by four Microsoft Dataverse custom tables and is published in Tablet format (1366 &times; 768).</p>

<p>As of the published export (<b>12 February 2026</b>), the application contains:</p>
<ul>
    <li><b>2 screens</b>: a default scaffold screen (<code>Screen1</code>) and a functional Ideas Dashboard (<code>scrIdeasDashboard</code>)</li>
    <li><b>4 Dataverse tables</b> connected: AI Ideas, AI Idea Assessments, AI Prompts, AI Prompt Ratings</li>
    <li><b>App-level initialisation</b>: current user context, score threshold variable, and score-mapping collection</li>
    <li><b>Ideas Dashboard</b>: a searchable, filterable gallery displaying ideas from the AI Ideas table with colour-coded status badges</li>
</ul>

<div class="callout">
<b>Note:</b> This BRD documents the application exactly as it exists in the exported <code>IdeasAPP_Powerapps.zip</code> package. It reflects only implemented functionality, not planned future screens or features.
</div>

