<h3>2.2 Data Connections</h3>
<p>The application connects to a single Dataverse environment (<code>default.cds</code>) and references four custom tables:</p>
<table>
<tr><th>Power Apps Name</th><th>Entity Set Name</th><th>Logical Name</th><th>Writable</th></tr>
<tr><td>AI Ideas</td><td>cr39e_aiideas</td><td>cr39e_aiidea</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td>AI Idea Assessments</td><td>cr39e_aiideaassessments</td><td>cr39e_aiideaassessment</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td>AI Prompts</td><td>cr39e_aiprompts</td><td>cr39e_aiprompt</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
<tr><td>AI Prompt Ratings</td><td>cr39e_aipromptratings</td><td>cr39e_aipromptrating</td><td>Yes</td></tr>
</table>

<p>Two sample/static data sources also exist (auto-generated by Power Apps):</p>
<table>
<tr><th>Name</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Writable</th></tr>
<tr><td>DropDownSample</td><td>Default sample data for dropdown controls (values: 1, 2, 3)</td><td>No</td></tr>
<tr><td>CustomGallerySample</td><td>Default sample data for gallery template (SampleHeading, SampleImage, SampleText)</td><td>No</td></tr>
</table>

<h3>2.3 Enabled Features</h3>
<p>The following Power Apps preview/feature flags are enabled in the application:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Performance optimisation enabled</li>
    <li>Delay-load screens</li>
    <li>Delay control rendering</li>
    <li>Formula data prefetch</li>
    <li>Native CDS experimental connector</li>
    <li>Dataverse actions enabled</li>
    <li>Non-blocking OnStart rule</li>
    <li>Error handling</li>
    <li>Canvas App runtime Copilot enabled</li>
    <li>Support column names as identifiers</li>
</ul>

