<h2>4. Data Model (Dataverse)</h2>

<p>All four custom tables use the publisher prefix <code>cr39e_</code>. The columns below are extracted directly from the application package metadata.</p>

<h3>4.1 AI Ideas (<code>cr39e_aiidea</code>)</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>Display Name</th><th>Logical Name</th><th>Type</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
<tr><td>AI Idea (PK)</td><td>cr39e_aiideaid</td><td>Unique Identifier</td><td>Primary key (GUID)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Name</td><td>cr39e_name</td><td>Single line of text</td><td>Primary name column (auto-generated)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Title</td><td>cr39e_title</td><td>Single line of text</td><td>Idea title</td></tr>
<tr><td>Description</td><td>cr39e_description</td><td>Multiple lines of text</td><td>Idea description</td></tr>
<tr><td>AI Capability Area</td><td>cr39e_aicapabilityarea</td><td>Choice</td><td>8 values (see Section 7)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Business Function</td><td>cr39e_businessfunction</td><td>Choice</td><td>11 values (see Section 7)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Expected Benefits</td><td>cr39e_expectedbenefits</td><td>Multiple lines of text</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td>Submitter Name</td><td>cr39e_submittername</td><td>Single line of text</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td>Submitter Email</td><td>cr39e_submitteremail</td><td>Single line of text</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td>Status</td><td>cr39e_status</td><td>Choice</td><td>11 values (see Section 7)</td></tr>
<tr style="background-color:#F0F0F0;"><td colspan="4"><i>System columns: statecode (Active/Inactive), statuscode (Active/Inactive), createdon, modifiedon, modifiedby, owningteam, versionnumber</i></td></tr>
</table>
<p><b>Relationship:</b> One-to-many &rarr; AI Idea Assessments (via <code>cr39e_Idea</code> lookup)</p>

