<h3>5.2 Screen1 (Scaffold)</h3>
<p>A blank screen created by the Power Apps template. Contains a vertical auto-layout root container (<code>ScreenContainer1</code>) with three child containers:</p>
<table>
<tr><th>Control Name</th><th>Control Type</th><th>Properties</th></tr>
<tr><td>ScreenContainer1</td><td>GroupContainer (AutoLayout)</td><td>Direction: Vertical, Gap: 16px, Padding: 16px all sides, Fill: RGBA(245,245,245,1)</td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;HeaderContainer1</td><td>GroupContainer (AutoLayout)</td><td>Direction: Horizontal, Height: 75px, Fill: White, Border-radius: 8px</td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;MainContainer1</td><td>GroupContainer (AutoLayout)</td><td>Direction: Vertical, Fill: White, Border-radius: 8px (flexible height)</td></tr>
<tr><td>&nbsp;&nbsp;FooterContainer1</td><td>GroupContainer (AutoLayout)</td><td>Direction: Horizontal, Height: 75px, Fill: White, Border-radius: 8px</td></tr>
</table>
<div class="callout-yellow">
<b>Observation:</b> All three containers are empty &mdash; no labels, buttons, or data-bound controls have been added to this screen.
</div>

<h3>5.3 scrIdeasDashboard (Implemented)</h3>
<p>The Ideas Dashboard is the primary functional screen. It contains 4 top-level controls:</p>

<h4>5.3.1 txtIdeasSearch</h4>
<table>
<tr><th>Property</th><th>Value</th></tr>
<tr><td>Control Type</td><td>Classic/TextInput@2.3.2</td></tr>
<tr><td>Position</td><td>X: 40, Y: 40</td></tr>
<tr><td>Default Text</td><td>"Search ideas..."</td></tr>
<tr><td>Font</td><td>Segoe UI</td></tr>
<tr><td>Border Colour</td><td>RGBA(245, 245, 245, 1)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Hover Border</td><td>RGBA(16, 110, 190, 1) &mdash; blue highlight on hover</td></tr>
</table>

<h4>5.3.2 ddStatusFilter</h4>
